The paper proposes a method for online log parsing using data mining techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE). The method involves encoding rules for parsing into a directed acyclic graph, which relates to data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of the method for system reliability management, which relates to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
